---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Learn Korean Through Food"
  description="About this site — a resource for people who love Korean food and want to learn Korean naturally through cooking."
>

  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="about-hero">
        <span class="eyebrow">About This Site</span>
        <h1>Why cook Korean food<br/><em>to learn Korean?</em></h1>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-main">
          <p class="lead">
            Learning Korean from a textbook is fine. But learning it while making
            <span class="kr">김치찌개</span> at midnight because you just binged another K-drama?
            That sticks.
          </p>

          <h2>The idea</h2>
          <p>
            Every recipe on this site is also a language lesson. You'll find the Korean name for
            every ingredient, the verbs used in each cooking step, and the grammar patterns that
            connect them — all explained in plain English for beginners.
          </p>

          <h2>Who is this for?</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>People curious about Korean food who want to understand the culture behind it</li>
            <li>Korean language learners who want real-world vocabulary (not just textbook Korean)</li>
            <li>K-drama fans who want to understand what characters are actually saying at the dinner table</li>
            <li>Anyone who finds cooking a more enjoyable classroom than Duolingo</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Resources we recommend</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.talk-to-me-in-korean.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Talk To Me In Korean</a> — the best structured Korean course online</li>
            <li><a href="https://www.90daykorean.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">90 Day Korean</a> — great for beginners building a foundation</li>
            <li><a href="https://papago.naver.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Naver Papago</a> — best Korean↔English translator</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <aside class="about-aside">
          <div class="aside-card">
            <h3>Quick Links</h3>
            <nav>
              <a href="/recipes">🍜 All Recipes</a>
              <a href="/learn">🇰🇷 Learn Korean</a>
              <a href="/ingredients">🧄 Ingredients Guide</a>
              <a href="/quizzes">🧠 Quizzes</a>
              <a href="/blog">📺 Culture & K-Drama</a>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <div class="aside-card legal-card">
            <h3>Legal</h3>
            <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
            <p class="disclaimer">
              This site participates in the Google AdSense program. Some links may be affiliate links.
              All recipe content is original and created for educational purposes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.about-wrap { padding:4rem 0 6rem; }
.container { max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem; }
.about-hero { margin-bottom:3.5rem; }
.eyebrow { display:block;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#C0392B;margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
.about-hero h1 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,3.5rem);color:#1A1A1A;margin:0;line-height:1.15; }
.about-hero h1 em { color:#C0392B; }

.about-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 280px;gap:4rem;align-items:start; }
.about-main .lead { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.8;color:#444;margin:0 0 2.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;border-bottom:2px solid #F0E6D3; }
.kr { font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:#C0392B; }
.about-main h2 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem; }
.about-main p { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:#555;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 1rem; }
.about-main ul { padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0 0 1rem; }
.about-main li { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:#555;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:0.35rem; }
.about-main a { color:#C0392B; }

.about-aside { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;position:sticky;top:80px; }
.aside-card { background:#fff;border:1px solid #e8e4de;border-radius:16px;padding:1.25rem; }
.aside-card h3 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin:0 0 0.75rem;padding-bottom:0.5rem;border-bottom:2px solid #F0E6D3; }
.aside-card nav { display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.3rem; }
.aside-card nav a { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.9rem;color:#555;text-decoration:none;padding:0.35rem 0.5rem;border-radius:6px;transition:background 0.15s,color 0.15s; }
.aside-card nav a:hover { background:#F0E6D3;color:#C0392B; }
.legal-card a { display:block;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.85rem;color:#C0392B;margin-bottom:0.75rem; }
.disclaimer { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.78rem;color:#aaa;line-height:1.6;margin:0; }

@media (max-width:768px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } .about-aside { position:static; } }
</style>
